13 SECTION 1. BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF MARYLAND,
14 That the Laws of Maryland read as follows:
15 Article – Education
16 2–305.1.
17 (A) (1) IN THIS SECTION THE FOLLOWING WORDS HAVE THE MEANINGS
18 INDICATED.
19 (2) “MINORITY STUDENT” HAS THE MEANING STATED IN
20 REGULATIONS ADOPTED BY THE STATE SUPERINTENDENT.
21 (3) “YOUTH SOCCER NONPROFIT ORGANIZATION” MEANS A
22 NONPROFIT ORGANIZATION THAT:
